{"tid":2395933,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺杜汶汗(杜狗)去到台灣餐餐都提撚住自己食咗幾錢勁撚戇鳩？(3 (第三個post))","createTime":"2021-02-05T08:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T10:48:26.000Z","uid":73381,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"58183ded9d5c88fd90cac258fd79dec1c2af7c3f","tid":2395933,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"台灣好幸褔？林夕點破勞工辛酸：港人遊台勿動不動說「太划算了」<br />\n<br />\n台灣人幸福嗎？物價低廉，吃好喝好，不少香港人到台灣旅遊都會燃起羨慕的心，甚至有移民的衝動。<span class=\"red\"><strong>不過著名作詞人林夕，兩年多前開始台港兩邊走，卻發現港人所不知道的真相，他指「東西好便宜」這句話，背後卻是台灣勞工低薪的代價，「你口中的蜂蜜，不小心會變成台灣朋友的鹽巴」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yeNgfpG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyeNgfpG.png&h=d07902cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcVxybo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcVxybo.png&h=59cbae5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kshThC5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkshThC5.png&h=e2c38a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S2FtjBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS2FtjBJ.jpg&h=76a85086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p8qdvJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp8qdvJo.jpg&h=0469dfaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09987183db662835f1a05dd8d6ed2e629354a8a6","tid":2395933,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:24:41.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤口中的蜂蜜，不小心會變成台灣朋友的鹽巴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4249a9493b0c894320fdc7842ec9d034292fec8","tid":2395933,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces